snippet.title: Carnivores Ice Age 2 - Evergreen Marsh preview
snippet.description: This is a preview of a new map I'm working on for my next fullgame Carnivores mod, Carnivores Ice Age 2. In addition, you get to see two new species as well. Special thanks to Poharex for making the Dodo model and Ornithomimid 1 for animating it.  The Mastodon was modeled by Poharex and the animations were done by ibuildcircuits. And sorry you didn't get to see the marshes in this video. But trust me they're there. It's unfortunate I had so much framerate stutter though.
